{{Infobox Company |name = Hartlepool Water |logo = Hartlepool Water (logo).png |type = |foundation = 1846 |location_city = |location_country = [[Huntingdon]], [[Cambridgeshire]], [[England]] |location = <!--modifies "Headquarters" entry--> |locations = <!--# of locations--> |key_people = |area_served = |industry = [[water supply|Water Supply]] |products = |services = |revenue = |operating_income = |net_income = |num_employees = |parent = |divisions = |subsid = |homepage = [http://www.hartlepoolwater.co.uk/ www.hartlepoolwater.co.uk] |dissolved = |footnotes = }}
'''Hartlepool Water''' is a water company that covers the town of [[Hartlepool]] in [[County Durham]] and surrounding area in the North East of England. Since 1997 it has been owned by [[Anglian Water]].<ref name=Who>{{cite web|title=Who We Are|url=http://www.hartlepoolwater.co.uk/about-us/3E7D3857E79A43CC8E6A37106EA87C71.aspx|publisher=Hartlepool Water|accessdate=5 May 2012}}</ref>
Hartlepool Water does not provide [[sewerage]] services. These are provided by [[Northumbrian Water]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Your wastewater services|url=http://www.hartlepoolwater.co.uk/household/your-wastewater-services.aspx|publisher=Hartlepool Water|accessdate=5 May 2012}}</ref>
The company was originally formed as the Hartlepool Gas and Water Company in 1846,<ref name=Who/> was re-incorporated into Hartlepool Water Ltd in 1995 and its company name, though not brand and business name, was renamed in 2006 as Osprey Water Services Ltd of Anglian Water's head office (Registered Office) retaining company number 3017251.<ref>[http://www.companieshouse.gov.uk UK Companies House]</ref>
